reviewText: Most Legit and influential tutorials out there , keep em rockin Eaz One!!

As the title states, this is the BEST dvd on the topic of graffiti introduction I have ever seen created. EAZ One makes the entire dvd easy to follow and it's completely visual style keeps you focused throughout.

The bonus fotage could stand alone as another dvd, but it just makes this one that much better.

HIGHLY RECOMMENDED
